{
  "stem": "27507.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But later on, the wall was built.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I think already in 1940, in the winter of 1940 to 1941.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that was a solid brick wall, which was probably well over two meters high with glass splinters embedded in the top layer so that it was very difficult to cross it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that was surrounding all of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I was going in ghetto to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But the school-- I don't remember it so terribly well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I know that I was going to-- in a street which was [POLISH] Street in the beginning, which was not very far from [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And there I was going to the-- maybe in '40/'41 in winter '40/'41 and until the end of spring '41.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I was going I think to the second class, elementary school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes, it was Jewish, because there was nobody else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think so, because if I would have learned any Yiddish or anything to do with the traditional things, I would have remembered it later, and I don't think I learned-- I certainly didn't learn anything remotely to do with religion or anything to do with Hebrew or anything to do with Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was a normal elementary school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I must have read about the-- learned or read about the stories of the Bible, because I knew the stories of the Bible.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew quite a bit of the Bible, of the early chapters and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that must have-- all of that must have been in Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but I don't think I learned about the Bible in the school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that was something that I learned-- I must have read, because I was reading a lot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could already read before the war started.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
